data.description: This property has beautiful views and is perched perfectly on top of a hill to accentuate the views. This property has so much to offer, it comes with a large shop, barn, corals, troughs, calving pens and much more. Approximately 10 acres are set up for cattle. There is a lot of information as to the current arrangement and an option of 22 acres that are ready for 5 acre building lots, so lets talk. There are so many opportunities with this property. The newer manufactured home has a beautiful wall of windows and a great open floor plan that consists of large vaulted ceilings, open kitchen and dinning. This lay out makes it perfect for entertaining guests and being able to stay involved. The master suit has vaulted ceilings and an adjoining master bath. The beautiful master bath contains a beautiful garden tub and a large walk in shower and yet there still is ample room to move around. Owner is willing to leave a lot of the farming related items for the new owner to help work the property. This is an opportunity you don't want to miss!
